trailingComments.value:
*
 * Rotate tree right. (see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tree_rotation)
 * /!\ This swaps the references to A and B.
 *
 *         B                A
 *        / \              / \
 *       A   c     ->     a   B
 *      / \                  / \
 *     a   b                b   c
 *
 *
 * @param {Node} B - The root of the tree.
 *
